    <div class="tab-content">
      <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane fade in active" id="our_story">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="col-lg-11 col-lg-offset-1"><p class="about-text-size-sub-heading">Our Story</p></div>
            <p>Three recent graduates set out to find the root of student engagement in the hopes of improving education for the next generation. They found that highly engaged students better understood their interests, strengths, and values, and made life decisions aligned with them.</p>
            <p>The evolution of enScholar would mirror the personal growth of each of the founders, who continued to seek out meaning and fulfillment in their own lives.</p>
            <p>Today, our team spans continents, cultures, and generations. We are truly a unique, passionate, and value-driven group that cares deeply about empowering today's youth.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <%= image_tag "story_image.png", class: "img-responsive" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane fade" id="our_mission">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="col-lg-11 col-lg-offset-1"><p class="about-text-size-sub-heading">Our Mission</p></div>
            <p><strong>The mission</strong> of the enScholar Educational Foundation is to help people live more meaningful, empowered lives, by facilitating a deeper understanding of themselves, so that they may, in turn, change the world for the better.</p>
            <p>Our aim is to revolutionize education and personal development by making them engaging, fun, and accessible to as many people as possible, regardless of location or economic status.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <%= image_tag "mission_image.png", class: "img-responsive" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
