            <p><strong>Website:</strong> <a class="about-text-primary" href="#">www.enscholar.com</a></p>
            <p><strong>25 words:</strong> enScholar is a non-profit changing how students find a career path through easy-to-use, video-guided tools that teach self-exploration and critical thinking.</p>
            <p><strong>50 words:</strong> enScholar is a non-profit changing how students find a career path through easy-to-use, video-guided tools that teach self-exploration and critical thinking. The self-directed, mobile-friendly system is currently being used in high school planning classes, and is designed to give parents an opportunity to play an active role.</p>
