      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <div class="tab-content text-muted about-margin-top-20">
          <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane fade in active" id="one">
            We promote, foster, and live out the mission and values of enScholar, not only in our work, but also in our personal lives. We are passionate about our vision, and put it above our own egos and self-interests.
          </div>
          <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane fade" id="two">
            We look for every opportunity to learn, improve, and advance. We seek to continuously evolve, and to understand ourselves more deeply, so that we can inspire and equip others to become better citizens of the world.
          </div>
          <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane fade" id="three">
            We demonstrate the courage to make mistakes and admit when we are wrong. We create an environment of encouragement and respect where we can be vulnerable and direct with each other.
          </div>
          <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane fade" id="four">
            We take pride in our work, we are driven, and we are tenacious. We care intensely about enScholar’s success, because of its potential to improve many lives now and in the future.
          </div>
          <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane fade" id="five">
            We listen and seek first to understand others’ points of view. We debate, discuss, and disagree in a manner which is respectful, courteous, and direct.
          </div>
          <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane fade" id="six">
            We lead and make decisions with the same openness that we encourage our users to have. We maintain the highest levels of integrity, hold ourselves and our teams accountable, and question any decision that doesn’t align with the enScholar values.
          </div>
          <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane fade" id="seven">
            We care about our team, and look for every opportunity to develop, support, and encourage each other. We proactively partner with others in the community and around the world who are aligned with our vision.
          </div>
        </div>
